Nothing
could
exceed
their
devotion
to
each
other.
There
was
some
discrepancy
in
age,
he
being
thirty
seven,
and
she
twenty
four;
but,
save
in
that
one
respect,
there
was
no
possible
objection
to
be
found
with
the
match.
The
engagement
was
in
February,
and
it
was
arranged
that
the
marriage
